    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "In the [tourism example](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/examples/tourism/), we solved that by doing:\n\n``` css\n    .ais-range-slider--handle-lower {\n      transform: translateX(-50%);\n    }\n\n    .ais-range-slider--handle-upper {\n      transform: translateX(50%);\n    }\n```\n\nI wonder if we should do that by default, thoughts?\n",
